{"tid":878620,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《造星》組男團出碟","createTime":"2018-10-27T09:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T09:31:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70df4223deec5efc3abf6058c376ae2c5d1ad156","tid":878620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20181027/20531786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181027%2F20531786&d=SjSrfsubTY%2Blp9nyk2rNPW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6b4ef4a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181027%2F20531786&h=df388189\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20181027/20531786</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月27日 <br />\n<br />\n《造星》組男團出碟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181027/large/27ec2p20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181027%2Flarge%2F27ec2p20.jpg&h=ae57a8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nViuTV傳將《全民造星》參賽者組成男團，自資出碟。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nViuTV舉辦的《Good Night Show全民造星》已經圓滿結束，坊間有不少唱片公司都對冠軍姜濤虎視眈眈，希望招攬成為旗下藝人，《蘋果》收到最新消息，原來ViuTV決定組成男團自資出唱片，成員除了冠軍姜濤、亞軍陳卓賢（Ian）和季軍楊樂文（Lokman）外，還有Anson Kong（江熚生）、肥仔梁業、Stanley（邱士縉）、Jeremy（李駿傑）、Edan（呂爵安），以及十強止步的Anson Lo（盧瀚霆）和小評（蔡港評），不過龍志權決定不簽約，細貓（應智越）因為仍在韓國讀書，以及與內地經理人公司合約未解決而沒有參與。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181027/large/27ec2p21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181027%2Flarge%2F27ec2p21.jpg&h=62fda843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜濤自成為《造星》冠軍後，工作多多。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181027/large/27ec2p29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181027%2Flarge%2F27ec2p29.jpg&h=b118b3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAnson Lo雖然十強止步，不過仍「入圍」成男團成員。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nViuTV計劃下周六舉行大型發佈會宣佈此事，《蘋果》昨日聯絡姜濤，但未有回覆，《造星》監製花姐（黃慧君）說：「我未係好清楚，等公司公佈啦。」Lokman亦好口密說：「好多嘢仲傾緊，我想做演員多啲。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：魯吉  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n推介中環空地免費聽歌　陳奕迅叫霆鋒讓路　紅館開跨年騷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\nF.I.R.拆夥換新主音"},{"pid":"8d407f79d2ff1603a89205f858a4c273694ffe00","tid":878620,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T09:31:06.000Z","msg":"不了 收視比勁歌金曲仲低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}